{"tid":2239704,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港台工會促交代重啟調查利君雅理據 質疑管方對人不對事","createTime":"2020-10-12T07:03:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T07:56:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a5a0863aa92b8df7edc939da457c8726dbb23059","tid":2239704,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:03:22.000Z","msg":"香港電台《視點31》主持利君雅上月底被延長試用期120日，並重啟有關投訴她的調查。港台節目製作人員工會今午召開員工大會，要求管方交代重啟調查的理據，「是否所有需要通過試用期的同事都被重新審視表現，還是今次是對人不對事？」<br />\n<br />\n員工大會今午在港台舉行，廣播處長梁家榮、負責處理重啟調查一事的副處長兼政務官馮建業，數十名包括新聞部和電視部等員工均有出席。<br />\n<br />\n工會指，針對利君雅的投訴個案，梁家榮、時任副處長陳敏娟、助理處長區麗雅及傳訊組總監伍曼儀組成的小組，已完成有關調查，確認投訴不成立並已向利君雅進行coaching（輔導），調整其提問技巧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/PX3JQSPK2BHCLGSWDKZ5PDITAU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2FPX3JQSPK2BHCLGSWDKZ5PDITAU%2F&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBTIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=8fb60836\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2FPX3JQSPK2BHCLGSWDKZ5PDITAU%2F&h=ff4fb650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/PX3JQSPK2BHCLGSWDKZ5PDITAU/</a>"},{"pid":"32d5635292c68d84d250cc5d0557fe360d861135","tid":2239704,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:05:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc3dde385800cc53d365f6f997bb0fabc78d99e6","tid":2239704,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32d5635292c68d84d250cc5d0557fe360d861135","tid":2239704,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:05:10.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589aee2d9c50aa2d9004e1bf4907fdf7bd529aee","tid":2239704,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb14cb2caca03e2d7034a77bb3dcfd1e8870eb7","tid":2239704,"uid":43062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:06:28.000Z","msg":"撐雅雅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f2ea483f65eddb9dfa21414b787a63fe7773ae","tid":2239704,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:06:52.000Z","msg":"試用咗成年，再延長三個用會睇到乜？"},{"pid":"0b4dee4d3d3d515550c9f05973c179b5c3ea4ccc","tid":2239704,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d891e3f8e9aaa8b3b4130f48401340713a310022","tid":2239704,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:56:14.000Z","msg":"調整其提問技巧<br />\n<br />\n有需要調整？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}